<section class="bg-white py-16 sm:py-20">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 sm:text-4xl">The Gold Standard in Home Financing</h2>
      <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-gray-600">
        A Conventional Loan is the go-to for most qualified homebuyers, offering flexibility and long-term savings that government-backed loans can't match.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="mt-12 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 text-center items-stretch">
      <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg border-2 border-[#bf9f5c]">
        <h3 class="font-bold text-xl text-[#09143e]">Conventional Loan</h3>
        <i class="fa-solid fa-handshake text-4xl text-[#bf9f5c] my-4" aria-hidden="true"></i>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-left text-gray-600">
          <li class="flex"><i class="fa-solid fa-check text-green-500 mr-2 mt-1" aria-hidden="true"></i><strong>PMI Is Cancellable:</strong> PMI may be removed once you reach an equity level that meets investor or lender guidelines.</li>
          <li class="flex"><i class="fa-solid fa-check text-green-500 mr-2 mt-1" aria-hidden="true"></i><strong>Flexible Property Types:</strong> Suitable for primary residences, second homes, and investment properties.</li>
          <li class="flex"><i class="fa-solid fa-check text-green-500 mr-2 mt-1" aria-hidden="true"></i><strong>Potential for Lower Overall Cost:</strong> May offer a lower total cost over time depending on the borrower’s scenario.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg border">
        <h3 class="font-bold text-xl text-gray-800">FHA Loan (Government-Backed)</h3>
        <i class="fa-solid fa-house-flag text-4xl text-gray-500 my-4" aria-hidden="true"></i>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-left text-gray-600">
          <li class="flex"><i class="fa-solid fa-times text-red-400 mr-2 mt-1" aria-hidden="true"></i><strong>MIP for Life:</strong> Mortgage insurance typically lasts for the full loan term.</li>
          <li class="flex"><i class="fa-solid fa-times text-red-400 mr-2 mt-1" aria-hidden="true"></i><strong>Primary Residence Only:</strong> Not eligible for second homes or investment properties.</li>
          <li class="flex"><i class="fa-solid fa-times text-red-400 mr-2 mt-1" aria-hidden="true"></i><strong>Higher Insurance Cost:</strong> Includes both upfront and monthly premiums.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

